      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "貂蝉上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00002",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "引子",
      "speakers": [
        "貂蝉"
      ],
      "text": "一频一笑总关情，暗自伤心曲。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00003",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "貂蝉"
      ],
      "text": "奴家貂蝉。想爹爹将我送与太师成妾，连日伏待，今日无一事，不免到凤仪亭，耍息一回，以消闷怀。来此已是凤仪亭，不免口占一词。",
      "text_length": 60
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00004",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "貂蝉"
      ],
      "text": "酒醉凤仪亭，凤凰不见来。乌鸦入凤群，独自闷忧怀。",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00005",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "貂蝉"
      ],
      "text": "那边好似温侯。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00006",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "吕布上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00007",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "吕布"
      ],
      "text": "我且躲在一旁，听她说些什么。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00008",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "吕布听。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00009",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "锁南枝",
      "speakers": [
        "貂蝉"
      ],
      "text": "妾命薄，泪暗流，无媒径路羞错走。勉强侍衾绸。见人还自丑，叹沉溺谁援手，我欲见温侯。啊呀，温侯吓，怎能勾？",
      "text_length": 52
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00010",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "锁南枝",
      "speakers": [
        "吕布"
      ],
      "text": "青青柳，姣又柔，一枝已折在他人手。把往事付东流，良缘叹非偶。簪可惜双凤头，这玉连环空在手。",
      "text_length": 45
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00011",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "貂蝉"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀，温侯吓，你好负心也！",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00012",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "吕布"
      ],
      "text": "怎说我负心？",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00013",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "貂蝉"
      ],
      "text": "想我爹爹送奴与温侯成亲，不知你往哪里去了？",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00014",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "吕布"
      ],
      "text": "虎牢关上收兵去了。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00015",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "貂蝉"
      ],
      "text": "及见狂且。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00016",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "吕布"
      ],
      "text": "住了，哪个是狂且？",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00017",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "貂蝉"
      ],
      "text": "就是太师！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00018",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "吕布"
      ],
      "text": "他便怎样？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00019",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "貂蝉"
      ],
      "text": "他便顿起不良之心，把我邀入府中淫污，我恨不得一死。今日得见温侯，哎呀，死亦瞑目也。",
      "text_length": 41
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00020",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "吕布"
      ],
      "text": "依小姐待要如何？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00021",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "貂蝉"
      ],
      "text": "但凭温侯。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00022",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "吕布"
      ],
      "text": "咳，只恨我虎牢关上来迟了！",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00023",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "红衲袄",
      "speakers": [
        "吕布"
      ],
      "text": "只指望上秦楼吹凤箫，又谁知抱琵琶弹别调。香褪了含宿雨梨花貌，带宽了舞东风杨柳腰。不能勾画春山眉黛巧，羞见你转秋波颜色姣。早知道相见难为情思也，何不当初不见高。",
      "text_length": 79
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00024",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "貂蝉"
      ],
      "text": "温侯吓！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00025",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "红衲袄",
      "speakers": [
        "貂蝉"
      ],
      "text": "你只图虎牢关上功绩高，顿忘了凤头簪恩爱好。同心带，急嚷嚷被他扯断了。玉连环，矻碀碀想你捶碎了。我今若不与温侯同到老，愿死在池中恨始消。",
      "text_length": 67
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00026",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "吕布"
      ],
      "text": "今生不得与你为夫妻，非盖世英雄也！",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00027",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "红衲袄",
      "speakers": [
        "貂蝉"
      ],
      "text": "若念夫妻情义，也把我尸骇覆草茅。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00028",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "貂蝉"
      ],
      "text": "温侯请上，受奴一拜。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00029",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "吕布"
      ],
      "text": "小将也有一拜。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00030",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内白",
      "speakers": [
        "董卓"
      ],
      "text": "貂蝉。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00031",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "董卓上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00032",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "董卓"
      ],
      "text": "吓，你不是吕布么？",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00033",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "吕布"
      ],
      "text": "正是吕布。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00034",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "貂蝉下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00035",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "董卓"
      ],
      "text": "反了反了。你不在虎牢关上干正事，来在凤仪亭中戏我的爱姬。戏我的爱姬是何道理？",
      "text_length": 38
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00036",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "吕布"
      ],
      "text": "那王司徒将貂蝉许配于我，是你谋占！",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00037",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "董卓"
      ],
      "text": "住了，哪个谋占？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00038",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "吕布"
      ],
      "text": "是你谋占！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00039",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "董卓"
      ],
      "text": "放屁！前番待你多亲近，把我爱姬来调引。巧弄拙，做出这般行径！",
      "text_length": 30
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00040",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "吕布"
      ],
      "text": "什么叫“行径”？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00041",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "董卓"
      ],
      "text": "你把我当什么人看待？",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00042",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "吕布"
      ],
      "text": "不过是义父罢了！",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00043",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "董卓"
      ],
      "text": "却又来！既称父子昧彝伦，顿叫人心中发恨。真发恨，把那方天画戟留下了残生！",
      "text_length": 36
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00044",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "吕布"
      ],
      "text": "今天怒尤恨，怒尤恨。既称父子美议论，美议论。何必起这心中留占！",
      "text_length": 31
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00045",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "董卓"
      ],
      "text": "哪个留占？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00046",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "吕布"
      ],
      "text": "是你留占。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00047",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "董卓"
      ],
      "text": "哦。是我留占。哈哈，你来你来吓！",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00048",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "吕布"
      ],
      "text": "休得要笑中藏刃。笑中藏刃，顿起人心中发硬。不念父子恩深，把方天画戟了残生，了残生！",
      "text_length": 41
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00049",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "吕布下，李儒上。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00050",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李儒"
      ],
      "text": "不要动手，不要动手！",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00051",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 51,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "董卓"
      ],
      "text": "好奴才，好奴才！",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00052",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 52,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李儒"
      ],
      "text": "我是李、是李儒。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00053",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 53,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "董卓"
      ],
      "text": "还是吕布？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00054",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 54,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李儒"
      ],
      "text": "我是李儒。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00055",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 55,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "董卓"
      ],
      "text": "哎吓！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00056",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 56,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李儒"
      ],
      "text": "吓。太师为何这等着恼？",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00057",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 57,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "董卓"
      ],
      "text": "反了反了！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00058",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 58,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李儒"
      ],
      "text": "点兵剿捕。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00059",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 59,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "董卓"
      ],
      "text": "哎，不是吓。那吕布反了！",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00060",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 60,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李儒"
      ],
      "text": "啊？怎么反了？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00061",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 61,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "董卓"
      ],
      "text": "他不在虎牢关上干正事，来在凤仪亭中戏我的爱姬，戏我的爱姬！",
      "text_length": 29
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00062",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 62,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李儒"
      ],
      "text": "吓，太师，可记得楚庄王的故事？",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00063",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 63,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "董卓"
      ],
      "text": "哎，这奴才，忙碌碌讲起故事来了！",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00064",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 64,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李儒"
      ],
      "text": "吕布既爱貂蝉，太师何不赐之？",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00065",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 65,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "董卓"
      ],
      "text": "奴才怎讲？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00066",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 66,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李儒"
      ],
      "text": "何不赐之？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00067",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 67,
      "seq_in_scene": 67,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "董卓"
      ],
      "text": "放屁，我的爱姬赐与吕布，你的妻子可能让于他？",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00068",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 68,
      "seq_in_scene": 68,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李儒"
      ],
      "text": "我的不能。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00069",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 69,
      "seq_in_scene": 69,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "董卓"
      ],
      "text": "你的不能，我的倒能？快快传李肃前来！",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00070",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 70,
      "seq_in_scene": 70,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李儒"
      ],
      "text": "有请李肃将军。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00071",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 71,
      "seq_in_scene": 71,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "李肃上。李儒下。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00072",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 72,
      "seq_in_scene": 72,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "李肃"
      ],
      "text": "忽听太师唤，慌忙到跟前。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00073",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 73,
      "seq_in_scene": 73,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李肃"
      ],
      "text": "参见太师。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00074",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 74,
      "seq_in_scene": 74,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "董卓"
      ],
      "text": "狗才狗才！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00075",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 75,
      "seq_in_scene": 75,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "董卓打李肃。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00076",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 76,
      "seq_in_scene": 76,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李肃"
      ],
      "text": "为何打起小人来了？",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00077",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 77,
      "seq_in_scene": 77,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "董卓"
      ],
      "text": "你举荐的好人吓！",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00078",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 78,
      "seq_in_scene": 78,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李肃"
      ],
      "text": "我荐的哪个？",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00079",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 79,
      "seq_in_scene": 79,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "董卓"
      ],
      "text": "那吕布不是你荐的么？",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00080",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 80,
      "seq_in_scene": 80,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李肃"
      ],
      "text": "荐的不差。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00081",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 81,
      "seq_in_scene": 81,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "董卓"
      ],
      "text": "他不在虎牢关前镇守，来在府中凤仪亭上戏我的爱姬。戏我的爱姬是何道理？",
      "text_length": 34
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00082",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 82,
      "seq_in_scene": 82,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李肃"
      ],
      "text": "太师，吕布既爱貂蝉，何不赐之？",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00083",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 83,
      "seq_in_scene": 83,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "董卓"
      ],
      "text": "你家的妻子肯让与人罢！过来，你去到那王司徒家中，问他貂蝉送与吕布，就不该送与太师；既送与太师，就不该送与吕布。吓，一个人送将来不明不白，弄得我父子，终朝每日，吃醋咽酸，是何道理？",
      "text_length": 89
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00084",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 84,
      "seq_in_scene": 84,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李肃"
      ],
      "text": "是。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00085",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 85,
      "seq_in_scene": 85,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "董卓"
      ],
      "text": "分得明白便罢，分不明白，将首级回府！",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00086",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 86,
      "seq_in_scene": 86,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李肃"
      ],
      "text": "得令。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00087",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 87,
      "seq_in_scene": 87,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "李肃下。貂蝉上。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00088",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 88,
      "seq_in_scene": 88,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "expression",
      "mode_label": "哭",
      "speakers": [
        "貂蝉"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀……",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00089",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 89,
      "seq_in_scene": 89,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "貂蝉"
      ],
      "text": "掩面悲啼，自恨泪珠弹。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00090",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 90,
      "seq_in_scene": 90,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "董卓"
      ],
      "text": "看你泪珠垂，似梨花一枝。卿为何低了头，倒到在人怀里，全不念礼义纲常，是和非。",
      "text_length": 38
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00091",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 91,
      "seq_in_scene": 91,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "貂蝉"
      ],
      "text": "哎，太师，想我爹爹，将奴送进相府，伏侍太师。我今日梳妆已毕，来到凤仪亭游玩散闷。不料那狂厮赶来，调戏于我。正要投池自尽，幸亏太师到来，救了奴的性命。",
      "text_length": 74
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00092",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 92,
      "seq_in_scene": 92,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "董卓"
      ],
      "text": "想你爹爹，将你送与吕布为妻，你跟他去罢。",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00093",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 93,
      "seq_in_scene": 93,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "貂蝉哭。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00094",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 94,
      "seq_in_scene": 94,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "貂蝉"
      ],
      "text": "我爹爹送奴与太师为妾，我不愿跟随吕布的了。",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00095",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 95,
      "seq_in_scene": 95,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "红衲袄",
      "speakers": [
        "貂蝉"
      ],
      "text": "勿使啼恨，新郎弃再嫁他人。汝再作恋新弃旧，汝再作恋新弃旧，一旦恩情付与他人。怜我不修礼，是恩情付于流水。",
      "text_length": 52
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00096",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 96,
      "seq_in_scene": 96,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "董卓"
      ],
      "text": "快随吕布去罢。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00097",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 97,
      "seq_in_scene": 97,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "貂蝉"
      ],
      "text": "太师好。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00098",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 98,
      "seq_in_scene": 98,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "董卓"
      ],
      "text": "我老了。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00099",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 99,
      "seq_in_scene": 99,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "貂蝉"
      ],
      "text": "太师不老。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00100",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 100,
      "seq_in_scene": 100,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "董卓"
      ],
      "text": "那吕布好吓。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00101",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 101,
      "seq_in_scene": 101,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "貂蝉"
      ],
      "text": "吓，太师好吓。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00102",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 102,
      "seq_in_scene": 102,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "貂蝉哭。董卓学貂蝉语。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00103",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 103,
      "seq_in_scene": 103,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "董卓"
      ],
      "text": "“哎吓，太师吓……”起来。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00104",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 104,
      "seq_in_scene": 104,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "貂蝉"
      ],
      "text": "多谢太师。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00105",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 105,
      "seq_in_scene": 105,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "董卓"
      ],
      "text": "下次不可。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00106",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 106,
      "seq_in_scene": 106,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "貂蝉"
      ],
      "text": "我们哪里安身才好？",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00107",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 107,
      "seq_in_scene": 107,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "董卓"
      ],
      "text": "我想眉坞郡安然，那里有三十年粮饷，四十万藤甲兵，皇家宫院，城池坚固。大事成就，封你为妃。",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00108",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 108,
      "seq_in_scene": 108,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "貂蝉"
      ],
      "text": "多谢太师。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00109",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 109,
      "seq_in_scene": 109,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "董卓"
      ],
      "text": "内使们，往眉坞去者。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01009003_e00110",
      "play_id": "01009003",
      "scene_id": "01009003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 110,
      "seq_in_scene": 110,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "〖尾声〗，貂蝉、董卓同下。",
      "text_length": 13
    }
  ],
  "roles_inferred": true
}